    }
}
```

This second query use a [`top_hits`](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/7.4/search-aggregations-metrics-top-hits-aggregation.html) aggregation to retrieve the documents grouped by `eId`. The returned documents are sorted by decreasing timestamp value so the documents having the max timestamp will be firsts, but you may also get documents with different timestamps.

